### 3.2 Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[User Device] -->|Encrypted| B[API Gateway]
    B --> C{Authentication}
    C -->|Valid| D[Application Server]
    C -->|Invalid| E[Reject]
    
    D --> F{Request Type}
    F -->|Mood Check-In| G[Process & Store]
    F -->|AI Chat| H[AI Service]
    F -->|Peer Support| I[Moderation Service]
    
    G --> J[(Encrypted DB)]
